Package gtu.graph

Interface GraphInterface<T extends java.lang.Comparable>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Graph
    public interface GraphInterface<T extends java.lang.Comparable>
    Interface to specify a GraphInterface ADT. A graph is a set of vertices and a set of edges. Vertices are represented by integers from 0 to n - 1 Edges are ordered pairs of vertices. Each implementation of the GraphInterface interface should provide a constructor that specifies the number of vertices and whether or not the graph is directed.
